sub_title: Creative Producer | Project Lead, at the forefront of design and innovation
summary:
A high integrity, customer focused, results driven Industrial Design professional with over 25 years experience in a global B2B environment. Understands international organizations, cultural differences and able to build the collaborations, networks and contacts necessary for success. 

Specialties:
- Early Phase Project definition
- Innovation management / New Product Development
- Stakeholder Alignment and Cross Disciplinary Project Management.
- Key Enabling Methodolgies https://www.clicknl.nl/kems/
- Design methodologies like Design Thinking, Scrum (Certified Scrum Master), Co Creation and Lean Startup
- Conceptual studies (including people value, technology and business opportunities)
- Immersive experiences
- Sustainability
